In the system it's neccesary to be able to:

Add a new customer.
Add a new order.
Add a new recipie.
Produce a new pallet.
Add ingredients to storage.
Subtract ingredients from storage upon creation of a pallet.
Block pallets from sale.
Remove a recipie.
Make deliveries of pallets. (Adding orderID to a pallet and increasing Quantity delivered in orderDetails).
